name: code.revelc.net
tagline: Random open source software for the public good.
body:
### Welcome to code.revelc.net

We are an ad-hoc group of internet citizens developing open source software for the public good. These are smaller projects, which aren't part of a larger community.

Our projects include:

* [apilyzer-maven-plugin][1]
* [zookeeper-maven-plugin][2]
* [gnome-keyring-java][3]

[1]: /apilyzer-maven-plugin
[2]: /zookeeper-maven-plugin
[3]: https://github.com/revelc/gnome-keyring-java

### Support or Contact
Send a message to @ctubbsii
